\" />"},{"pid":"b48753a6e3d1f08190dc371d28d005c3e8ada911","tid":1063840,"uid":215844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"相比起辛苦 我更驚冇錢生存<br />\n<br />\n唔係生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921abd315a2b207a861c4fdb191db9a1c2326f40","tid":1063840,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"有時放工買飯 見到做餐飲既做到無停都真係幾慘<br />\n企左成日 手又無停"},{"pid":"cc5f07ae298a64112f7241958bd70dbc678362ac","tid":1063840,"uid":227691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:43:58.000Z","msg":"係好攰，不過一邊做一邊食補返數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe04ed44c44587bab567be9acc5b7dc8ed1b8b9","tid":1063840,"uid":62506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:46:38.000Z","msg":"辛苦工通常係今日事今日了，準時開工，準時收工，唔需要思考太多，日日都差唔多"},{"pid":"85af962b249c89fe367d91050c21a2b9204dfc9b","tid":1063840,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"我都做過,一日就頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係唔捱得,而係覺得果份人工買我做呢D野係唔抵"},{"pid":"70caba1879cea8f1952aea7b0929273a3aebe765","tid":1063840,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"我做過<br />\n初初做都還好<br />\n但每日做重覆不需思考既動作<br />\n唔駛幾日就會覺得人生好灰<br />\n不斷諗呢種日子幾時先可以完結<br />\n但你好快就知係冇得完結只會無限loop<br />\n跟住又返返上面覺得人生好灰<br />\n不斷諗呢種日子幾時先會完結既狀態<br />\n直到你40年後65歲退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7132975e9adc8cc62d8edba7b1dcd5e46d5883b1","tid":1063840,"uid":191312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"我今日心情好！撚！曳！"},{"pid":"7b36728a3e8bd593f0b855e726944fae9e7d718d","tid":1063840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}